Stealth Health Wellness Protocol
DAILY RULES
• Hydration: Drink exactly 3 Liters of water daily.
• Avoid caffeine after 2 PM.
• Sleep: Maintain an 8-hour sleep window.
• No screens 45 minutes before bed.
• Activity: Minimum 8000 steps daily.
• Stretch 10 minutes every morning.
• Log meals within 30 minutes of eating.
• Never skip two days in a row.
• Consistency beats perfection.
DAY-BY-DAY GUIDANCE
• Day 1: Welcome + hydration baseline + sleep review.
• Day 2: Hydration adherence + meal logging.
• Day 3: Consistency + sleep quality + caffeine rules.
• Day 4: Progress review + obstacle identification.
• Day 5+: Accountability + long-term habits.
IMPORTANT NOTES
• Consistency beats perfection.
• Track daily.
• Listen to your body.
